nodes.text: Attack on a Venator-class Star Destroyer

During the Clone Wars, a super tank was sent to a Venator-class Star Destroyer. However, once aboard the Star Destroyer, the B1-Series battle droids inside the tank began an attack on the cruiser, destroying its cargo bay. With the clone troopers unable to stop the tank, Commander Jet sent a Jedi Knight to destroy the tank and the enemy battle droids.
